祝贺「Fate/Grand Order」简中版9周年！

怀揣着与英灵们并肩战斗的过往，将心意寄托于未来的旅途。

御主们，庆典时刻现在开始！

축 · 한국 페이트/그랜드 오더 5주년!!


이것은, 당신과 함께 걷는 이야기.
지금까지 지나온 여로와
앞으로 펼쳐질 새로운 여정을 생각하며
그 발걸음을 이어간다.

축 · 한국 페이트/그랜드 오더 6주년!!

이것은, 당신과 함께 걷는 이야기.
지금까지 지나온 여로와
앞으로 펼쳐질 새로운 여정을 생각하며
그 발걸음을 이어간다.

한국 페이트/그랜드 오더 7주년.
7년간의 여정과 함께한 모든 분께 감사를.

수많은 미래의 이야기를 이겨 내고, 
뒤를 돌아보면 떠오르는, 소중하고 행복한 시간들.

지금 걷는 이 길의 여정에 무엇이 기다릴지 알 수 없으나,
확실한 것은 단 하나.

앞으로도 당신과 함께───

「Fate/Grand Order」繁中版6週年快樂！

如同沙礫一粒一粒堆積，御主們的信念也隨著歲月的積累更加堅定。
即使面對艱困逆境，也從未放棄前進的腳步。

懷抱著「奪回屬於我們的未來」的決心，繼續探索前方的未竟之地吧。

「Fate/Grand Order」繁中版7週年快樂！

一起出發吧，踏上冒險的旅程！
鮮為人知的景色等著我們去探索，
在臺北車站集合，和英靈們共襄盛舉。
迦勒底7週年，與你攜手邁向未來！

Fate/Grand Order」繁中版8週年快樂！

摩天輪與旋轉木馬交相輝映，
隨著夜空璀璨煙火，進入繽紛幻想世界，
齊聚兒童新樂園，和英靈們共享絢爛輝煌。
迦勒底8週年，夢幻慶典歡笑無限！

Congratulations to the English version of "Fate/Grand Order" for reaching its 3rd anniversary!

Our journey has been a memorable one, and we will continue to follow our path, wherever it may take us.

Happy 3rd Anniversary!

Congratulations to the English version of "Fate/Grand Order" for reaching its 4th anniversary!

Today we're going to let our hair down and celebrate.

Let's enjoy the 4th anniversary celebration!

Congratulations to the English version of "Fate/Grand Order" for reaching its 5th anniversary!

Our stargazing journey continues.

As we celebrate and reflect on the path we have taken, we pray that the journey ahead will continue to be fulfilling and delightful.

Congratulations to the English version of "Fate/Grand Order" for reaching its 6th anniversary! Chaldea is in a celebratory mood on this extraordinary and joyous occasion. As we look back on our journey so far and look ahead to the journey yet to come, let's begin the 6th anniversary celebration!

Congratulations to the English version of "Fate/Grand Order" for reaching its 7th anniversary! Let's carry all the memories we've made with us as we make our way to the end of the rainbow. May this year's anniversary be an unforgettable one!

Congratulations to the English version of "Fate/Grand Order" for reaching its 8th anniversary! With this brief respite as motivation, let's continue down the road to the unknown. Here's to 8 years and to new meetings.
